channel.title: [718 loading 742] Yellowscape, where your dreams come true!
channel.description:
Hello and welcome to our advertisement thread! We are a truelly community driven server, we have big big updates on Fridays, and we are always working on something for you!
Official forums: Yellowscape.com
Play now! https://www.dropbox.com/s/rk3udpo307cggcv/YellowScape.jar?dl=0
We have over 200+customs, active players and staff :D
I have many pictures of unique aspects of our server! enjoy!
We are also looking for loyal and dedicated players, server is new, first day of release, join now and level up
Staff is also needed, but has to be earned! :D
